@startuml
skinparam componentStyle rectangle

|User Traffic| as UT

[Traffic Allocation] as TA
[Control Group] as CG
[Experiment Group] as EG
[Metrics Collection] as MC
[Statistical Test] as ST
[Decision] as DEC

UT --> TA: Random Split
TA --> CG: Variant A
TA --> EG: Variant B

CG --> MC: Control Metrics
EG --> MC: Experiment Metrics
MC --> ST: Comparison Analysis
ST --> DEC: Launch/ Rollback

note right of ST
  - Significance testing
  - Confidence interval
  - Effect size
end note

note left of DEC
  Full rollout
  Continue testing
  Rollback
end note

@enduml
